You play a cat that builds a campground for other cats. You build tents and cabins for them to sleep in and amenities for them to enjoy. A hot springs. A library. And you craft things to make it a better place and give your cat more energy to do more stuff. And just when you think you've run out of things to do, you can unlock new areas to do more things in! Awesome! Edit: Updated review due to bug fix and increased rating to five stars!
